1. Clone + Setup DNS
Tambahkan A-record traefik.hafizhsp.site â†’ IP server

2. Create Folder letsencrypt
mkdir -p letsencrypt
touch letsencrypt/acme.json
chmod 600 letsencrypt/acme.json

3. Copy ENV
cp .env.example .env

4. Running
docker network create edge
docker compose up -d

5. Cek Log
docker logs -f edge-traefik


6. Verifikasi
# pastikan argumen sudah benar (harus ada tlschallenge, ada redirections, tidak ada httpchallenge)
docker inspect edge-traefik --format '{{json .Args}}' | tr ',' '\n' | egrep 'acme|entrypoints|challenge|redirections'

# cek HTTP -> redirect ke HTTPS
curl -I http://halohub.id
# cek HTTPS normal
curl -I https://halohub.id

# (opsional) dashboard
open https://traefik.hafizhsp.site
